title: Discussion Thread: Biden Delivers Remarks on 2024 Budget Proposal at 2:30 p.m. ET
author: PoliticsModeratorBot
text:
**Background Reporting:**

- CBS: [Biden releases 2024 budget proposal with eye toward reelection bid](https://www.cbsnews.com/live-updates/biden-budget-white-house-medicare-social-security-deficit/)

- Philadelphia Inquirer (metered paywall): [President Joe Biden to speak in Northeast Philly today; budget would increase child tax credit and Pell Grants](https://www.inquirer.com/news/philadelphia/live/joe-biden-philadelphia-speech-budget-time-road-closures-20230309.html)

- NPR: [Biden is using his budget as a cudgel in the debt ceiling fight — and for 2024](https://www.npr.org/2023/03/09/1161967948/biden-is-using-his-budget-as-a-cudgel-in-the-debt-ceiling-fight-and-for-2024)

**Primary Sources:**

- Assorted WhiteHouse.gov 'Briefing Room' [pages on the budget release](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/), including the ones dedicated to 1) [Medicare and healthcare](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/07/fact-sheet-the-presidents-budget-extending-medicare-solvency-by-25-years-or-more-strengthening-medicare-and-lowering-health-care-costs/), 2) [equity](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-president-bidens-budget-advances-equity/), 3) [tribal nations and communities](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-president-bidens-budget-delivers-for-tribal-nations-and-tribal-communities/), 4) [inflation](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-president-bidens-budget-lowers-costs-for-families-and-gives-the-american-people-more-breathing-room/), 5) [the border and immigration](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-president-bidens-budget-strengthens-border-security-enhances-legal-pathways-and-provides-resources-to-enforce-our-immigration-laws/), 6) [energy, climate, and environmental justice](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-president-bidens-budget-lowers-energy-costs-combats-the-climate-crisis-and-advances-environmental-justice/), 7) the [federal customer service experience](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-president-bidens-budget-improves-customer-experience-and-service-delivery-for-the-american-people/), 8) [public safety and crime](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-president-bidens-budget-makes-our-communities-safer-and-combats-crime/), 9) [veterans and their families](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-president-bidens-budget-honors-our-nations-sacred-commitment-to-veterans-and-military-families/), 10) [housing](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-president-bidens-budget-lowers-housing-costs-and-expands-access-to-affordable-rent-and-home-ownership/), 11) [global challenges](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-president-bidens-budget-keeps-america-safe-and-confronts-global-challenges/), 12) ["Wasteful Spending", combating systemic fraud, and program cost efficacy](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-the-presidents-budget-cuts-wasteful-spending-on-big-pharma-big-oil-and-other-special-interests-cracks-down-on-systemic-fraud-and-makes-programs-more-cost-effective/), and 13) [the deficit](https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/03/09/fact-sheet-the-presidents-budget-cuts-the-deficit-by-nearly-3-trillion-over-10-years/)

**Where to Watch:**

- C-SPAN: [President Biden gives remarks in Philadelphia on the release of his budget request for fiscal year 2024.](https://www.c-span.org/video/?526614-1/president-biden-unveils-budget-proposal-speech-philadelphia)

- The White House on YouTube: [President Biden Delivers Remarks on his Budget for Fiscal Year 2024](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qpJnCELX3Ag)
